"{\"uid\": \"outlookindia.com-art-entertainment-k-drama-watch-bts-jin-carries-the-olympic-torch-in-paris-ahead-of-summer-olympics-2024\", \"text\": \"Get magazine delivered to your doorstep  Get latest issue delivered instantly  Only in Delhi-NCR, Mumbai, Bengaluru, Pune, Lucknow & Kolkata  Get magazine delivered to your doorstep  Get latest issue delivered instantly  Only in Delhi-NCR, Mumbai, Bengaluru, Pune, Lucknow & Kolkata  Ahead of the Paris Olympics 2024,BTS' Jin was selected as the torchbearer for the event. Recently, he scripted history as he carried the Olympic flame in Paris just a few weeks before the Summer Olympics. He carried the torch at the Louvre Museum as he represented the Republic of Korea. The videos from the event have gone viral on social media.  Reports mention thatJinleft forParison July 11 from Seoul. The flame was first lit in Olympia, Greece on April 16, 2024. It is expected to reach Paris on July 26 for the opening night of the Olympics. Approximately 10,000 torchbearers, including Jin, are taking part in the torch relay, which will cover 400 cities across France and several overseas regions as well. In past Olympics, notable torchbearers have included Muhammad Ali at the 1996 Atlanta Games and David Beckham at the 2012 London Games. Coincidentally, Jin carried the torch on Bastille Day, the French National Day.  Take a look at the videos of Jin with the Olympic torch here.  11 days to go until#Paris2024! \\ud83c\\uddeb\\ud83c\\uddf7\\ud83d\\udc40 Watch the Torch get closer and closer with@bts_bighitJin \\ud83d\\udd25@Paris2024pic.twitter.com/zZ2rHiTTRX  [#\\uc624\\ub298\\uc758\\ubc29\\ud0c4] The Olympic Games, Paris 2024 with#Jin\\uc131\\ud654\\ub9cc\\ud07c\\uc774\\ub098 \\ub530\\ub4ef\\ud558\\uace0 \\ub208\\ubd80\\uc168\\ub358 \\uc9c4\\ud83d\\udd25#\\uc624\\ub298\\uc758\\uc9c4#Jin#\\uc9c4#BTS#\\ubc29\\ud0c4\\uc18c\\ub144\\ub2e8#\\uc62c\\ub9bc\\ud53d#Olympics#\\ud30c\\ub9ac2024#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/x60dHP7soa  The viral videos have left fans proud of Jin's achievement. Reacting to the video, one fan said, \\\"Can not wait to watch my favorite sports! Proud of Jin for helping kick off the Summer Olympics.\\\" A second fan commented, \\\"We are so extremely proud of Kim Seokjin\\u2026 pls congratulate him on successfully completing his role asOlympic GamesTorchbearer\\u2026the torch burned brightly for him!\\\" A third fan mentioned, \\\"SO PROUD OF YOU JIN\\u2026Thank you for your hard work.\\\"  On the work front, Jin was recently discharged from his mandatory military duty. He is also set to release a solo album and a variety show this year.    BYOutlook Entertainment Desk  Click/Scan to Subscribe  Video | Tamasha At 10: Aged Like Fine Wine Or Spoilt Like Milk?  Video | Why Bihar Votes The Way It Does: Caste, Migration & 2025 Election Trends  WATCH | Subir Sinha Raises Questions Over Anomalies in Bihar Election Counting  Video | Nowgam Police Station Blast: 9 Dead in Accidental Srinagar Explosion During Handling of Seized Explosives  Hugh Grant Expresses His Desire To Do A Bollywood Film; Wants To See His The Bengali Night Co-Star Supriya Pathak Again  Akhanda 2: Makers Of Nandamuri Balakrishna Starrer Apologise For The Delay; New Release Date To Be Announced Soon  Dhurandhar 2 Release Date Confirmed: Ranveer Singh's Film To Clash With Yash's Toxic  Netflix To Acquire Warner Bros. For $82.7 Billion, Writers Guild Of America Opposes The Deal  Kalamkaval Box Office Collection Day 1: Mammootty Starrer Crime Thriller Earns Over Rs 4 Crore  Nationwide Travel Chaos as IndiGo Cancels Over 400 Flights  India Vs South Africa, 3rd ODI: See Best Photos From Visakhapatnam's ACA-VDCA Cricket Stadium  Day In Pics: December 06, 2025  New Zealand Vs West Indies, 1st Test Day 5: Justin Greaves Double Ton Snatches Draw For WI  Copyright \\u00a9 2025 Outlook Publishing India Pvt Ltd.  Copyright \\u00a9 2025 Outlook Publishing India Pvt Ltd. All pages of the Website are subject to our terms and conditions and 